s://www.nytimes.com/2019/12/12/arts/music/harry-styles-camila-cabello-review.html|archive-date=2019-12-12|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="The Guardian">{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2019/nov/04/50-great-tracks-for-november-from-dua-lipa-destroyer-selena-gomez-and-more|title=50 great tracks for November from Dua Lipa, Destroyer, Selena Gomez and more|last1=Beaumont-Thomas|first1=Ben|last2=Snapes|first2=Laura|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2019-11-04|access-date=2020-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404223535/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2019/nov/04/50-great-tracks-for-november-from-dua-lipa-destroyer-selena-gomez-and-more|archive-date=2020-04-04|url-status=live}}</ref>。[[副歌|副歌]]有[[靈魂樂|靈魂樂]]合唱團墊音<ref name="irishtimes">{{cite web|url=https://www.irishtimes.com/culture/music/harry-styles-fine-line-review-a-journey-of-sex-sadness-and-self-discovery-1.4109330|title=Harry Styles: ''Fine Line'' review – A journey of sex, sadness and self-discovery|last=Bruton|first=Louise|work=[[愛爾蘭時報|The Irish Times]]|date=2019-12-13|access-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191213120113/https://www.irishtimes.com/culture/music/harry-styles-fine-line-review-a-journey-of-sex-sadness-and-self-discovery-1.4109330|archive-date=2019-12-13|url-status=live}}</ref>，因此《[[獨立報|獨立報]]》的羅森·奧康納（{{lang|en|Roisin O'Connor}}）表示曲目有〈[[加州之夢|加州之夢]]〉風格和[[迷幻音樂|迷幻樂]]韻味<ref name="theindependent"/>，而《{{tsl|en|Slate (magazine)|板巖 (雜誌)|板巖}}》的克里斯·莫蘭菲（{{lang|en|Chris Molanphy}}）稱這首歌是「縹緲和聲加上輕柔撥弄的海灘樂」<ref name="slate">{{cite web|url=https://slate.com/culture/2020/08/harry-styles-watermelon-sugar-first-hot-100-number-one.html|title=Why Harry Styles Just Scored His First No. 1 Song|last=Molanphy|first=Chris|work=Slate|date=2020-08-14|access-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814204519/https://slate.com/culture/2020/08/harry-styles-watermelon-sugar-first-hot-100-number-one.html|archive-date=2020-08-14|url-status=live}}</ref>。

〈聚光之下〉整體創作為多段[[分解聯奏|分解聯奏]]的前副歌和後副歌，以及一段[[副歌|副歌]]，捨棄了傳統歌曲架構<ref name="idvice">{{cite web|url=https://i-d.vice.com/en_us/article/ywaxpw/harry-styles-new-sexy-video-lights-up|title=Harry Styles is back and his new video is sexy as hell|last=Kheraj|first=Alim|work=i-D|date=2019-10-11|access-date=2020-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191123004639/https://i-d.vice.com/en_us/article/ywaxpw/harry-styles-new-sexy-video-lights-up|archive-date=2019-11-23|url-status=live}}</ref>。歌曲拉开序幕是長達17秒的樂器演奏，接著到第19秒時，歌手順著節拍開始演唱首段正歌。第28秒吉他聲讓音高飄移，斯泰爾斯也隨之唱出調適過的緊緻聲音<ref name="soundonsound"/>。他的歌聲在前副歌變得失真<ref name="pitchfork"/><ref name="independent">{{cite web|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/reviews/harry-styles-fine-line-album-review-tracklist-songs-one-direction-brit-awards-a9340646.html|title=Harry Styles review, ''Fine Line'': Dextrous, audacious album just a little too in thrall to music's greats|last=Pollard|first=Alexandra|work=[[獨立報|The Independent]]|date=2020-02-17|access-date=2020-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200604122141/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/reviews/harry-styles-fine-line-album-review-tracklist-songs-one-direction-brit-awards-a9340646.html|archive-date=2020-06-04|url-status=live}}</ref>。[[音樂術語列表|快節奏]]的正副歌在第1分18秒開始，為重複的主音旋律和歌詞，而且唱每句前都會有以「Shine」為開頭的合聲<ref name="soundonsound"/>。曲目在尾奏前有短暫[[強弱法|漸強]]<ref name="idvice"/>。歌曲使用多種人聲[[織體_(音樂)|織體]]，將高低[[八度|八度]]的聲線交織在一起<ref name="soundonsound">{{cite web|url=https://www.soundonsound.com/people/mix-review-january-2020|title=The Mix Review: January 2020|last=Senior|first=Mike|work=Sound on Sound|date=2020-01|access-date=2020-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191221094034/https://www.soundonsound.com/people/mix-review-january-2020|archive-date=2019-12-21|url-status=live}}</ref>。奧康納稱斯泰爾斯的聲線「出乎意料地輕快」，與他早年作品「更清晰的演唱方式」形成鮮明對比<ref name="theindependent"/>。《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》<ref name="bbinterview">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/8533762/harry-styles-lights-up-five-burning-questions/|title=Five Burning Questions: ''Billboard'' Staffers Discuss How Harry Styles 'Lights Up' the Hot 100 at No. 17 This Week|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|date=2019-10-21|access-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017045302/https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/8533762/harry-styles-lights-up-five-burning-questions/|archive-date=2019-10-17|url-status=live}}</ref>、《[[衛報|衛報]]》<ref name="The Guardian"/>、{{tsl|en|MTV News|MTV新聞}}<ref name="MTV">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/3142030/harry-styles-lights-up-video/|title=Harry Styles launches a (very wet and very shirtless) new era with 'Lights Up'|last=Roth|first=Madeline|publisher=MTV News|date=2019-10-11|access-date=2020-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329084821/http://www.mtv.com/news/3142030/harry-styles-lights-up-video/|archive-date=2020-03-29|url-status=live}}</ref>和《紐約時報》的樂評人將歌曲的音樂風格與迷幻樂團{{tsl|en|Tame Impala|溫馴高角羚樂團|溫馴高角羚}}拿來作比較<ref name="newyork"/>，而《新音樂快遞》和《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》則覺得它聽起來像節奏藍調流行歌手[[賈斯汀·提姆布萊克|賈斯汀·提姆布萊克]]的早年作品<ref name="nmetrack"/><ref name="Variety"/>。

〈聚光之下〉的歌詞有關自我發現和自我認同<ref name="paper"/><ref name="MTV"/><ref name="nmetrack">{{cite web|url=https://www.nme.com/reviews/harry-styles-lights-up-track-review-second-album-single-2556245|title=Harry Styles' new track 'Lights Up' trades rock'n'roll excess for a lighter touch|last=Hunt|first=El|work=[[新音乐快递|NME]]|date=2019-10-11|access-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225143802/https://www.nme.com/reviews/harry-styles-lights-up-track-review-second-album-single-2556245|archive-date=2019-12-25|url-status=live}}</ref>。部分樂評人認為這首歌是評述斯泰爾斯的名氣<ref name="theindependent"/><ref name="ewrev"/>。斯泰爾斯在歌曲中擁抱自我，唱道：「Lights up and they know who you are / Know who you are / Do you know who you are?」（大意：聚光之下他們就知道你是誰/知道你是誰/但你知道你是誰嗎？）<ref name="paper">{{cite web|url=https://www.papermag.com/harry-styles-lights-up-video-2640929048.html?rebelltitem=14#rebelltitem14|title=Harry Styles Is Drenched, Tripping and Maybe Coming Out in His New Video|last=Goldfine|first=Jael|work=Paper|date=2019-10-11|access-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119080927/https://www.papermag.com/harry-styles-lights-up-video-2640929048.html?rebelltitem=14|archive-date=2021-01-19|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="nmetrack"/>副歌的歌詞有他對自己的揭露：「Step into the light ... I'm not ever going back」（大意：站進光芒中……我不會再回去）<ref name="guardian"/>。《衛報》的勞拉·斯內普斯（{{lang|en|Laura Snapes}}）認為他透過「矛盾的內心獨白」來表達，而歌詞中有「他和前任在空窗期時各說各話」<ref name="guardian"/>。《{{tsl|en|Now (newspaper)|現在報}}》的雷·麥克納馬拉（{{lang|en|Rea McNamara}}）認為歌曲是「講述自愛和放手的簡短頌詩」<ref name="Now">{{cite web|url=https://nowtoronto.com/music/album-reviews/harry-styles-fine-line/|title=Review: Harry Styles is a more responsible Internet Boyfriend on ''Fine Line''|last=Mcnamara|first=Rea|work=Now|date=2019-12-13|access-date=2019-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191213142942/https://nowtoronto.com/music/album-reviews/harry-styles-fine-line/|archive-date=2019-12-13|url-status=live}}</ref>，而《[[紐約_(雜誌)|禿鷲]]》的克雷格·詹金斯（{{lang|en|Craig Jenkins}}）覺得它是關於「用璀璨的光芒穿透我們心中的黑暗」<ref name="vulture"/>。《{{tsl|en|Tallahassee Democrat|塔拉赫西民主報}}》的賈·阿隆索（{{lang|en|Jia Alonso}}）和《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》的郭安英（{{lang|en|Anying Guo}}）將歌曲歌詞和斯泰爾斯的[[性取向|性取向]]聯繫起來<ref name="td">{{cite news|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/78789000/tallahassee-democrat/|title=Harry Styles (finally) releases new music|last=Alonso|first=Jia|work=Tallahassee Democrat|page=19|date=2019-10-14|access-date=2021-04-24|via=Newspapers.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210602091202/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/78789000/tallahassee-democrat/|archive-date=2021-06-02|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="wp">{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/arts-entertainment/2019/12/13/how-harry-styles-navigated-solo-stardom-one-direction-fine-line/|title=How Harry Styles navigated solo stardom, from One Direction to ''Fine Line''|last=Guo|first=Anying|work=[[華盛頓郵報|The Washington Post]]|date=2019-12-13|access-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191214200315/https://www.washingtonpost.com/arts-entertainment/2019/12/13/how-harry-styles-navigated-solo-stardom-one-direction-fine-line/|archive-date=2019-12-14|url-status=live}}</ref>。《{{tsl|en|Paper (magazine)|紙 (雜誌)|紙}}》和《[[時代_(雜誌)|時代]]》指出歌詞有種快陷入憂鬱的感覺<ref name="paper"/><ref name="time"/>。

==發行和推廣==
〈聚光之下〉發行前，斯泰爾斯在2019年10月10日[[世界精神衛生日|世界精神衛生日]]發起一場活動<ref name="W Magazine"/><ref name="wmhd">{{cite web|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/harry-styles-new-album-one-direction-fan-world-mental-health-day-twitter-a9151416.html|title=Harry Styles sends fan touching message on World Mental Health Day as he hints at new album|last=Michallon|first=Clémence|work=[[獨立報|The Independent]]|date=2019-10-10|access-date=2021-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191011031441/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/harry-styles-new-album-one-direction-fan-world-mental-health-day-twitter-a9151416.html|archive-date=2019-10-11|url-status=live}}</ref>。倫敦和紐約的數塊廣告牌上印著[[哥倫比亞唱片|哥倫比亞唱片]]標誌和「你知道你是誰？」（{{lang|en|Do You Know Who You Are?}}）標語<ref name="Variety">{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/music/news/harry-styles-new-music-lights-up-1203367044/|title=Harry Styles Drops New Single 'Lights Up' – Variety|last1=Nickolai|first1=Nate|last2=Aswad|first2=Jem|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|date=2019-10-11|access-date=2019-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191011041319/https://variety.com/2019/music/news/harry-styles-new-music-lights-up-1203367044/|archive-date=2019-10-11|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="mtvtour">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/3141872/harry-styles-teases-do-you-know-who-you-are-posters/|title=Do You Know What These Mysterious Harry Styles Posters Mean?|last=Tilchen|first=Jordyn|publisher=MTV News|date=2019-10-10|access-date=2019-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191010222349/http://www.mtv.com/news/3141872/harry-styles-teases-do-you-know-who-you-are-posters/|archive-date=2019-10-01|url-status=live}}</ref>，還帶有首字母縮略字「TPWK」（全稱「以善待人」），此句早在{{tsl|en|Harry Styles: Live on Tour|哈利·斯泰爾斯：現場巡演}}的周邊商品就出現過<ref name="mtvtour"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/looks-like-harry-styles-teasing-new-album-do-you-know-who-you-are-2555811|title=It looks like Harry Styles is teasing his new album|last=Reilly|first=Nick|work=[[新音樂快遞|NME]]|date=2019-10-10|access-date=2019-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191010150717/https://www.nme.com/news/music/looks-like-harry-styles-teasing-new-album-do-you-know-who-you-are-2555811|archive-date=2019-10-10|url-status=live}}</ref>，甚至後來透露是《搖滾界線》[[以善待人|其中一首歌曲的標題]]<ref name="tpwk">{{cite web|url=https://www.musicweek.com/talent/read/small-changes-make-a-big-difference-harry-styles-tells-the-story-of-treat-people-with-kindness/078397|title='Small changes make a big difference': Harry Styles tells the story of Treat People With Kindness|last=Homewood|first=Ben|work=Music Week|date=2019-12-12|access-date=2021-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308131235/https://www.musicweek.com/talent/read/small-changes-make-a-big-difference-harry-styles-tells-the-story-of-treat-people-with-kindness/078397|archive-date=2021-03-08|url-status=live}}</ref>。同時架設以「你知道你是誰？」命名的網站，所有輸入名字的用戶都會受到稱讚<ref>{{cite web|url=https://globalnews.ca/news/6021282/harry-styles-new-single-lights-up/|title=Harry Styles releases new single, 'Lights Up' — and he's shirtless in the video|last=Wallis|first=Adam|publisher=Global News|date=2019-10-11|access-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820111938/https://globalnews.ca/news/6021282/harry-styles-new-single-lights-up/|archive-date=2020-08-20|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.papermag.com/harry-styles-new-website-2640917768.html|title=Harry Styles' Mysterious Website Told Me I'm Fantastic|last=Wetmore|first=Brendan|work=Paper|date=2019-10-10|access-date=2019-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191011032927/https://www.papermag.com/harry-styles-new-website-2640917768.html|archive-date=2019-10-11|url-status=live}}</ref>。斯泰爾斯在[[Instagram|Instagram]]上載他自己的相片來宣布歌曲標題<ref name="ewrev">{{cite web|url=https://ew.com/music/2019/10/11/harry-styles-returns-with-new-bacchanalian-music-video-for-lights-out/|title=Harry Styles returns with new bacchanalian music video for 'Lights Up'|last=Lenkar|first=Maureen Lee|work=[[娛樂週刊|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2019-10-11|access-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191011193920/https://ew.com/music/2019/10/11/harry-styles-returns-with-new-bacchanalian-music-video-for-lights-out/|archive-date=2019-10-11|url-status=live}}</ref>。2019年10月11日，厄斯金唱片（{{lang|en|Erskine Records}}）和哥倫比亞唱片在多國以[[數位音樂下載|數位下載]]和[[流媒体|串流]]形式以《搖滾界線》首發單曲發行〈聚光之下〉<ref name="rsvideo"/><ref name="Apple Music"/>。同天，歌曲加進[[BBC廣播一台|BBC廣播一台]]歌單<ref name="ukradio">{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/articles/3tqPdBWF9yMbTrfjWvfKV8t/radio-1-playlist|title=Radio 1 Playlist|publisher=[[BBC廣播一台|BBC Radio 1]]|access-date=2019-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191012125717/https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/articles/3tqPdBWF9yMbTrfjWvfKV8t/radio-1-playlist|archive-date=2019-10-12}}</ref>，以及澳洲和義大利的[[當代流行電台|當代流行電台]]<ref name="ausradio">{{Cite web|url=https://themusicnetwork.com/charts/issues/1258/1258-singles-to-radio/|title=Singles to Radio|website=The Music Network|access-date=2019-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191023180038/https://themusicnetwork.com/charts/issues/1258/1258-singles-to-radio/|archive-date=2019-10-23|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="italyradio">{{Cite press release|url=http://radiodate.it/radio-date/harry-styles-lights-up-189814-11-10-2019-radiodate/|title=Harry Styles 'Lights Up' {{!}} (Radio Date: 11 October 2019)|last=Pagura|first=Chiara|publisher=[[索尼|Sony]]|access-date=2019-10-12|via=Airplay Control S.R.L.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191012170644/http://radiodate.it/radio-date/harry-styles-lights-up-189814-11-10-2019-radiodate/|archive-date=2019-10-12|url-status=live}}</ref>。2020年初，唱片公司在全球釋出特別版[[單曲|7英寸黑膠唱片]]，當中涵蓋全新[[A面與B面|B面]]歌曲〈你知道你是誰？ ({{tsl|en|Unusual types of gramophone records|不尋常黑膠唱片類型|閉紋}})〉<ref name="7-inch">{{Cite web|url=https://shopuk.hstyles.co.uk/products/lights-up-7-digital-download|title=Lights Up 7" + Digital Download|website=Harry Styles UK|access-date=2019-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191012170646/https://shopuk.hstyles.co.uk/products/lights-up-7-digital-download|archive-date=2019-10-12|url-status=dead}}</ref>。

